text: Dorogino () is a rural locality (a village) in Kirillovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 225 as of 2010. There are 26 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Ufa, 4 km from Kirillovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Dorogino, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
